# Title: Potential RDP Tunneling Via Plink
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-08-04
# Level: high
# Description: Execution of plink to perform data exfiltration and tunneling
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1572
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_plink_susp_tunneling.yml

(CommandLine="*:127.0.0.1:3389*" Image="*\\plink.exe") OR (CommandLine="*:3389*" Image="*\\plink.exe" CommandLine IN ("* -P 443*", "* -P 22*"))